{"title":"燃烧的火","authors":["南村"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":11,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧的火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用这具古老民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉默多年的火把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点燃我们的泪珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当旗帜和彩球飞舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请伸出手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反省一次次的迷失和悔悟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当国歌响起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是我们的灵魂和身躯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千千万万英雄和先烈的血液"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在歌唱中欢呼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖辈的骨骼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土地上执著的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些自西而东的江河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是我们一次次地穿越"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一次次地坎坷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当圣火燃着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们想起什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起一只苹果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被人们随意刀割"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起一只鸽子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所饱尝的饥饿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起一支笛管"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经流落的酸涩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当编钟从历史中埋没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当史书从焚烧中复活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们想起什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起圆明园的火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起冬天里的那把火——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只奔跑的马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所留下的蹄声和寂寞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群多么完美的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他们真正懂得了母亲的含义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗歌就会在他们眼里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿然壮丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们就会回忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那株梦中蓊郁的树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面的果子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个甜润"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们就会想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去做一个诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个诗人的定义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所负有的责任"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们衔起哨音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这个即将来临的辉煌的早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃亮我们的脉搏和青春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：山东淄博广播电视大学）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}